{
  "message": "feat(dashboard): add alert indicators to fleet page\n\nAdd alertChecker to dashboard Server and pass AlertCount to fleet template.\nThe Alerts tab now shows a red badge with the alert count when alerts exist.\nVM rows in all views (All VMs, By Repo, By Owner, Running) now:\n- Highlight with red background when they have alerts\n- Show a warning triangle icon next to the VM ID when alerts exist\n- Handle alert updates via WebSocket messages\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
